    <title>Hexo + next 定制个性化酷站</title>
    <link href="https://datapsyco.github.io/2018/01/23/Hexo-next-setup/"/>
    <id>https://datapsyco.github.io/2018/01/23/Hexo-next-setup/</id>
    <published>2018-01-23T07:41:47.000Z</published>
    <updated>2018-01-25T07:24:10.947Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p></p><p align="center"><em><code>Github</code> + <code>Hexo</code> + <code>Next</code> + <strong>你</strong> 打造一个个人风格的网站</em><br></p><br><a id="more"></a><p></p><h2 id="创建或使用github账号"><a href="#创建或使用github账号" class="headerlink" title="创建或使用github账号"></a>创建或使用<a href="https://www.github.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">github</a>账号</h2><ul><li><p>新建一个xxx.github.io(xxx与github用户名相同)的仓库.</p></li><li><p>生成并添加SSH-KEY</p></li></ul><p>本地安装<a href="https://git-scm.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">git</a></p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span><span class="bash"> ssh-keygen -t rsa -C <span class="string">"你的邮箱"</span></span></span><br><span class="line">Generating public/private rsa key pair.</span><br><span class="line">Enter file in which to save the key (/home/fdipzone/.ssh/id_rsa): 这里输入要生成的文件名</span><br><span class="line">Enter passphrase (empty for no passphrase):                       这里输入密码 </span><br><span class="line">Enter same passphrase again:                                      这里重复输入密码</span><br><span class="line">Your identification has been saved in /home/xxx/.ssh/id_rsa.</span><br><span class="line">Your public key has been saved in /home/xxx/.ssh/id_rsa.pub.</span><br><span class="line">The key fingerprint is:</span><br><span class="line">f2:76:c3:6b:26:10:14:fc:43:e0:0c:4d:51:c9:a2:b0 fdipzone@ubuntu</span><br><span class="line">The key's randomart image is:</span><br><span class="line">+--[ RSA 2048]----+</span><br><span class="line">|    .+=*..       |</span><br><span class="line">|  .  += +        |</span><br><span class="line">|   o oo+         |</span><br><span class="line">|  E . . o        |</span><br><span class="line">|      ..S.       |</span><br><span class="line">|      .o .       |</span><br><span class="line">|       .o +      |</span><br><span class="line">|       ...oo     |</span><br><span class="line">|         +.      |</span><br><span class="line">+-----------------+</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>将xxx.rsa.pub里的文件全复制下来，粘贴到github SSH-KEY添加页面的Key栏下，title自定义，保存。</p><h2 id="本地安装Node-js和Hexo"><a href="#本地安装Node-js和Hexo" class="headerlink" title="本地安装Node.js和Hexo"></a>本地安装Node.js和Hexo</h2><ul><li><p>安装<a href="https://nodejs.org/en/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Node.js</a></p></li><li><p>安装hexo</p></li></ul><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install npm install -g hexo-cli</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="搭建博客"><a href="#搭建博客" class="headerlink" title="搭建博客"></a>搭建博客</h2><h3 id="初始化"><a href="#初始化" class="headerlink" title="初始化"></a>初始化</h3><p>安装好 Hexo 后，先任意目录新建个文件夹，名字可以为 blog，然后进入这个文件夹，输入命令：</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash"> 所在目录：~/blog/</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo init</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>等待下载安装完成后,输入:</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash"> 所在目录：~/blog/</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo g</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">hexo s 或者 hexo s -p 3001(指定一个端口，默认是4000，如果4000已被占用可以加-p参数)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>然后浏览器访问点开 <a href="http://localhost:4000/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">http://localhost:4000/</a> ，恭喜你！已经在本地搭建好博客了，默认主题是landscape。接下来我们更换Next主题以及部署到github Pages。</p><h3 id="安装-Git-部署插件"><a href="#安装-Git-部署插件" class="headerlink" title="安装 Git 部署插件"></a>安装 Git 部署插件</h3><p>在站点文件夹根目录blog下输入以下命令：</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash"> 所在目录： ~/blog/</span></span><br><span class="line">npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>然后在根目录下的站点配置文件修改相关部署参数：</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 文件位置： ~/blog/_config.yml</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># URL</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 请将前缀换成你自己的</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">url:</span> <span class="attr">https://datapsyco.github.io/</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">...</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">...</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">...</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Deployment</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 将地址换成你的</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">deploy:</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">  type:</span> <span class="string">git</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">  repository:</span> <span class="attr">https://github.com/datapsyco/datapsyco.github.io.git</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">  branch:</span> <span class="string">master</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>将其中的<code>datapsyco</code>改成你的 Github 注册的帐号名就行，然后执行下面的命令：</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash"> 所在目录： ~/blog/</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo clean</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">hexo g  # generate</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">hexo d  # deploy</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash">或者使用hexo clean后使用hexo g -d</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>输入你的 Github 的用户名和密码，成功后复制<code>https://账户名.github.io/</code>到浏览器打开就行。嘿！你的博客就搭好了~</p><h2 id="下载Next主题"><a href="#下载Next主题" class="headerlink" title="下载Next主题"></a>下载<a href="https://github.com/iissnan/hexo-theme-nexti" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Next</a>主题</h2><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash"> 当前目录: ~/blog/</span></span><br><span class="line">git clone https://github.com/iissnan/hexo-theme-next themes/next</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="修改主题"><a href="#修改主题" class="headerlink" title="修改主题"></a>修改主题</h3><p>修改<code>站点</code>配置文件,将主题<code>theme</code>参数改成 <code>next</code></p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 文件位置： ~/blog/~config.yml</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">## Themes: https://hexo.io/thems/</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">theme:</span> <span class="string">next</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="修改站点配置文件"><a href="#修改站点配置文件" class="headerlink" title="修改站点配置文件"></a>修改站点配置文件</h3><p>添加站点<code>标题</code>、<code>描述</code>、<code>作者</code>、<code>网站语言</code>、<code>时区</code>等配置:</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 文件位置： ~/blog/_config.yml</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Site</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Site</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">title:</span> <span class="string">DataPsyco</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">subtitle:</span> <span class="string">Data</span> <span class="string">Code</span> <span class="string">Life</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">description:</span> <span class="literal">No</span> <span class="string">Data</span> <span class="literal">No</span> <span class="string">Life~</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">author:</span> <span class="string">datapsyco</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">language:</span> <span class="string">zh-Hans</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">timezone:</span> <span class="string">Asia/Shanghai</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="Next主题配置"><a href="#Next主题配置" class="headerlink" title="Next主题配置"></a>Next主题配置</h2><p>修改<code>next主题</code>配置文件，更多详细配置，请查阅<a href="http://theme-next.iissnan.com/getting-started.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Next官方文档</a>。</p><blockquote><p><code>主题</code>配置文件和<code>站点</code>配置文件名字都叫<code>_config.yml</code>,但是<code>主题</code>配置文件在<code>~/blog/themes/next/_config.yml</code>。修改时请多留意</p></blockquote><h3 id="修改网站标志favicon"><a href="#修改网站标志favicon" class="headerlink" title="修改网站标志favicon"></a>修改网站标志favicon</h3><ul><li>直接去 <a href="https://realfavicongenerator.net" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://realfavicongenerator.net</a></li><li>上传一张符合的图片</li><li>选项弄好后，下载压缩包，解压复制粘贴到`~/blog/source/images/ 里（没有images文件夹自己建）</li><li>最后记得要稍微改下文件名，与下面的保持一致(解压下来的问价没有带next,而默认有next那是next的标志)</li></ul><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 当前目录: ~/blog/themes/next/_config.yaml</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># To get or check favicons visit: https://realfavicongenerator.net</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Put your favicons into `hexo-site/source/` (recommend) or `hexo-site/themes/next/source/images/` directory.</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Default NexT favicons placed in `hexo-site/themes/next/source/images/` directory.</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># And if you want to place your icons in `hexo-site/source/` root directory, you must remove `/images` prefix from pathes.</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># For example, you put your favicons into `hexo-site/source/images` directory.</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Then need to rename &amp; redefine they on any other names, otherwise icons from Next will rewrite your custom icons in Hexo.</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">favicon:</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">  small:</span> <span class="string">/images/favicon-16x16.png</span>  <span class="comment"># 注意：默认是images/favicon-16x16-next.png, 替换成你的，下面也是</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">  medium:</span> <span class="string">/images/favicon-32x32.png</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">  apple_touch_icon:</span> <span class="string">/images/apple-touch-icon.png</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">  safari_pinned_tab:</span> <span class="string">/images/logo.svg</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">  android_manifest:</span> <span class="string">/images/manifest.json</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">  ms_browserconfig:</span> <span class="string">/images/browserconfig.xml</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="关键词、页脚设置"><a href="#关键词、页脚设置" class="headerlink" title="关键词、页脚设置"></a>关键词、页脚设置</h3><p>将相关的参数换成你的</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 当前目录: ~/blog/themes/next/_config.yaml</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">keywords:</span> <span class="string">"datapsyco, cgdeeplearn, python, spark, data science, blog, 博客, 数据, 机器学习, Hexo"</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Set rss to false to disable feed link.</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Leave rss as empty to use site's feed link.</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Set rss to specific value if you have burned your feed already.</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">rss:</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">footer:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># Specify the date when the site was setup.</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># If not defined, current year will be used.</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">#since: 2015</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">  since:</span> <span class="number">2017</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># Icon between year and copyright info.</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">  icon:</span> <span class="string">heart</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># If not defined, will be used `author` from Hexo main config.</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">  copyright:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># -------------------------------------------------------------</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># Hexo link (Powered by Hexo).</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">  powered:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">  theme:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment"># Theme &amp; scheme info link (Theme - NexT.scheme).</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">    enable:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment"># Version info of NexT after scheme info (vX.X.X).</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">    version:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># -------------------------------------------------------------</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># Any custom text can be defined here.</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">#custom_text: Hosted by &lt;a target="_blank" href="https://pages.github.com"&gt;GitHub Pages&lt;/a&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="设置菜单布局"><a href="#设置菜单布局" class="headerlink" title="设置菜单布局"></a>设